entry.title: This Part of Ukraine's Counteroffensive Is Pressing Forward, With Little Western Help
entry.content: Ukraine has retaken a handful of villages in the eastern Donetsk region, but the West is questioning Kyiv’s decision to attack on multiple axes.

entry.title: Young Japanese Find It Pays---Double---to Work Abroad
